<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>SPORTMATCH — 잘못된 요청</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..40,300;0,9..40,400;0,9..40,500;0,9..40,600;0,9..40,700;1,9..40,400&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500;700&family=Bebas+Neue&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
<%- include('partials/navbar') %>
<div class="error-page">
  <div class="error-bg-number">400</div>

  <div style="position:relative;z-index:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center">
    <div class="error-emoji">⚠️</div>
    <div class="error-code">400 · Bad Request</div>
    <div class="error-title">잘못된 요청이에요</div>
    <div class="error-desc">
      요청 형식이 올바르지 않아 서버가 처리할 수 없어요.<br>
      입력값을 다시 확인하고 재시도해 주세요.
    </div>
    <div class="error-actions">
      <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="history.back()">← 이전으로</button>
      <button class="btn btn-outline" onclick="location.href='/'">🏠 홈으로</button>
    </div>

    <% if (typeof message !== 'undefined' && message) { %>
    <div class="error-detail-box">
      <div class="error-detail-label">오류 상세</div>
      <div class="error-detail-text"><%= message %></div>
    </div>
    <% } %>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
